text: Anisley García (born 19 January 2002) is a Cuban diver. She competed in the women's 1 metre springboard event at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. She finished in 22nd place in the preliminary round. ==References== Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban female divers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Divers at the 2019 Pan American Games
